  <body dur="03:27.500">
    <div begin="00:01.090" end="03:27.500">
      <p begin="00:01.090" end="00:07.730" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L1"><span begin="00:01.090" end="00:02.200">今日</span><span begin="00:02.310" end="00:03.260">が</span><span begin="00:04.990" end="00:05.360">終</span><span begin="00:05.360" end="00:05.720">わ</span><span begin="00:05.760" end="00:06.000">り</span><span begin="00:06.160" end="00:06.700">な</span><span begin="00:06.790" end="00:06.940">の</span><span begin="00:07.040" end="00:07.730">か</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">今天是迎来了终结</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">今天是迎來了終結</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Is today the end</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">오늘이 끝나는 것인지</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Est-ce la fin aujourd'hui</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Si hoy es el final</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Ist heute das Ende</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Se hoje é o fim</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Сегодня это конец</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">È la fine di oggi</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Kyou ga owari na no ka</span></p>
      <p begin="00:09.560" end="00:13.590" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L2"><span begin="00:09.560" end="00:10.300">始</span><span begin="00:10.390" end="00:10.750">ま</span><span begin="00:10.770" end="00:11.110">り</span><span begin="00:11.160" end="00:11.460">な</span><span begin="00:11.580" end="00:12.550">の</span><span begin="00:12.670" end="00:13.590">か</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">还是拉开了序幕</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">還是拉開了序幕</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Or the beginning</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">시작되는 것인지</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Ou bien le commencement</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">O es el principio</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Oder der Anfang</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Ou se é o começo</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Или же начало</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">O è forse l'inizio</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Hajimari na no ka</span></p>
      <p begin="00:14.150" end="00:18.310" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L3"><span begin="00:14.150" end="00:14.530">こ</span><span begin="00:14.560" end="00:14.890">れ</span><span begin="00:14.940" end="00:15.300">じゃ</span><span begin="00:15.350" end="00:15.640">わ</span><span begin="00:15.730" end="00:16.070">か</span><span begin="00:16.190" end="00:17.100">ら</span><span begin="00:17.340" end="00:18.020">な</span><span begin="00:18.020" end="00:18.310">い</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">仅凭这样无法知晓</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">僅憑這樣無法知曉</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">I can't tell like this</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">이래서는 알 수 없어</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Comme ça je n'en sais rien</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Así no puedo saberlo</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">So kann ich es nicht wissen</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Desse jeito não consigo saber</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Так и не пойму</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Così non riesco a capirlo</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Kore ja wakaranai</span></p>
      <p begin="00:19.520" end="00:26.130" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L4"><span begin="00:19.520" end="00:20.460">咲</span><span begin="00:20.460" end="00:20.570">い</span><span begin="00:20.740" end="00:21.370">て</span><span begin="00:23.470" end="00:23.840">見</span><span begin="00:23.840" end="00:24.090">上</span><span begin="00:24.210" end="00:24.410">げ</span><span begin="00:24.440" end="00:24.600">る</span><span begin="00:24.680" end="00:25.470">頬</span><span begin="00:25.630" end="00:26.130">に</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">在绽放着仰望的脸颊上</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">在綻放著仰望的臉頰上</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">On the cheek looking up as it blooms</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">피어나 올려다보는 뺨에</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Sur mes joues qui s'épanouissent en regardant vers le haut</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">En las mejillas que florecen y miran hacia arriba</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Auf den blühenden aufschauenden Wangen</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Nas bochechas que desabrocham e olham para cima</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">На щеках что расцветают глядя вверх</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Sulle guance arrossate che guardano in alto</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Saite miageru hoho ni</span></p>
      <p begin="00:28.080" end="00:31.720" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L5"><span begin="00:28.080" end="00:28.720">温</span><span begin="00:28.860" end="00:29.180">も</span><span begin="00:29.230" end="00:29.590">り</span><span begin="00:29.590" end="00:29.800">を</span><span begin="00:29.800" end="00:29.920">受</span><span begin="00:30.030" end="00:30.930">け</span><span begin="00:31.200" end="00:31.720">て</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">感受着那份温暖</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">感受著那份溫暖</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Receiving warmth</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">온기를 받으며</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">En recevant cette chaleur</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Recibiendo calidez</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Die Wärme empfangend</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Recebendo o calor</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Ощутив тепло</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Ricevendo il tepore</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Nukumori o ukete</span></p>
      <p begin="00:32.660" end="00:36.240" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L6"><span begin="00:32.660" end="00:33.070">在</span><span begin="00:33.070" end="00:33.380">る</span><span begin="00:33.420" end="00:33.740">だ</span><span begin="00:33.820" end="00:34.170">け</span><span begin="00:34.210" end="00:34.330">の</span><span begin="00:34.400" end="00:34.510">こ</span><span begin="00:34.640" end="00:35.480">と</span><span begin="00:35.730" end="00:36.240">が</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">仅仅是存在于此</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">僅僅是存在於此</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Just simply existing</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">그저 존재한다는 것만이</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Le simple fait d'exister</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Porque el simple hecho de existir</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Weil einfach nur zu existieren</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">O simples fato de existir</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Одно лишь то что я просто существую</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Il solo fatto di esistere</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Aru dake no koto ga</span></p>
      <p begin="00:36.880" end="00:42.670" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L7"><span begin="00:36.880" end="00:37.220">究</span><span begin="00:37.280" end="00:37.580">極</span><span begin="00:37.690" end="00:37.890">と</span><span begin="00:37.890" end="00:38.250">思</span><span begin="00:38.250" end="00:38.370">え</span><span begin="00:38.470" end="00:38.750">て</span><span begin="00:38.750" end="00:38.860">し</span><span begin="00:38.900" end="00:39.430">ま</span><span begin="00:39.430" end="00:39.510">う</span><span begin="00:39.590" end="00:39.920">か</span><span begin="00:39.970" end="00:42.670">ら</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">就让人觉得这已是究极的圆满</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">就讓人覺得這已是究極的圓滿</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Because I end up thinking it is the ultimate thing</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">궁극의 의미라 생각되어 버리니까</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Me semble être l'ultime accomplissement</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Termina pareciéndome lo supremo</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Mir als das Ultimative erscheint</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Acaba parecendo ser o ápice para mim</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Кажется мне абсолютным пределом</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Mi sembra la cosa più assoluta</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Kyuukyoku to omoete shimau kara</span></p>
      <p begin="00:48.470" end="00:52.480" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L8"><span begin="00:48.470" end="00:49.230">安</span><span begin="00:49.230" end="00:49.600">ら</span><span begin="00:49.600" end="00:49.960">ぎ</span><span begin="00:50.000" end="00:50.270">の</span><span begin="00:50.360" end="00:50.640">最</span><span begin="00:50.790" end="00:51.800">中</span><span begin="00:51.930" end="00:52.480">で</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">在宁静的极境之中</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">在寧靜的極境之中</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">In the midst of tranquility</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">평온함의 한가운데서</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Au beau milieu de la quiétude</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">En medio de la tranquilidad</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Inmitten der tiefsten Geborgenheit</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">No meio da tranquilidade</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">В самом сердце покоя</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Nel mezzo della tranquillità</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Yasuragi no sanaka de</span></p>
      <p begin="00:53.060" end="00:56.970" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L9"><span begin="00:53.060" end="00:53.340">生</span><span begin="00:53.430" end="00:53.830">け</span><span begin="00:53.830" end="00:54.200">る</span><span begin="00:54.200" end="00:54.580">愛</span><span begin="00:54.610" end="00:55.090">の</span><span begin="00:55.170" end="00:55.340">手</span><span begin="00:55.390" end="00:56.540">触</span><span begin="00:56.540" end="00:56.970">り</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">鲜活爱意的触感</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">鮮活愛意的觸感</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">The touch of living love</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">살아 숨 쉬는 사랑의 감촉</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Le toucher d'un amour vivant</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">El tacto del amor viviente</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Die Berührung lebendiger Liebe</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">O toque do amor vivo</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Прикосновение живой любви</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Il tocco dell'amore vivo</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Ikeru ai no tezawari</span></p>
      <p begin="00:57.260" end="01:03.210" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L10"><span begin="00:57.260" end="00:57.620">そう</span><span begin="00:57.700" end="00:58.340">か</span><span begin="00:58.430" end="00:58.650">こ</span><span begin="00:58.680" end="00:58.800">れ</span><span begin="00:58.850" end="00:59.480">が</span><span begin="00:59.610" end="01:00.200">私</span><span begin="01:00.300" end="01:00.600">の</span><span begin="01:01.120" end="01:01.400">完</span><span begin="01:01.500" end="01:01.870">成</span><span begin="01:01.930" end="01:02.340">だ</span><span begin="01:02.340" end="01:02.570">っ</span><span begin="01:02.570" end="01:03.210">た</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">这样啊 这就是我所追寻的完整</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">這樣啊 這就是我所追尋的完整</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">I see this was my completion</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">그렇구나, 이것이 나의 완성이었어</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Je vois c'était donc ça ma complétude</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Ya veo así que esta era mi perfección</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Ah das war also meine Vollendung</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Entendo então esta era a minha completude</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Вот как значит это и было моим завершением</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Ah capisco era questa la mia completezza</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Souka kore ga watashi no kansei datta</span></p>
      <p begin="01:03.830" end="01:11.100" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L11"><span begin="01:03.830" end="01:04.380">人</span><span begin="01:04.940" end="01:05.530">生</span><span begin="01:06.130" end="01:06.440">を</span><span begin="01:06.840" end="01:08.450">遡</span><span begin="01:08.450" end="01:08.790">る</span><span begin="01:08.850" end="01:09.110">み</span><span begin="01:09.210" end="01:09.950">た</span><span begin="01:10.020" end="01:10.290">い</span><span begin="01:10.410" end="01:11.100">に</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">宛如溯流回溯人生一般</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">宛如溯流回溯人生一般</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">As if tracing back through life</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">인생을 거슬러 올라가듯</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Comme si je remontais le cours de ma vie</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Como si retrocediera en la vida</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Als würde ich das Leben zurückverfolgen</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Como se voltasse no tempo da vida</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Словно возвращаясь вспять по реке жизни</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Come per risalire la corrente della vita</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Jinsei o sakanoboru mitai ni</span></p>
      <p begin="01:11.510" end="01:15.430" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L12"><span begin="01:11.510" end="01:11.860">乳</span><span begin="01:11.860" end="01:12.190">白</span><span begin="01:12.250" end="01:12.520">の</span><span begin="01:12.620" end="01:13.040">線</span><span begin="01:13.040" end="01:13.550">を</span><span begin="01:13.630" end="01:14.410">辿</span><span begin="01:14.410" end="01:14.600">っ</span><span begin="01:14.600" end="01:14.950">た</span><span begin="01:14.990" end="01:15.430">ら</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">若是循着那乳白的丝线</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">若是循著那乳白的絲線</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">If I follow the opalescent line</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">유백색의 선을 따라가 보니</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">En suivant cette ligne d'un blanc laiteux</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Si sigo la línea de un blanco lechoso</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Wenn ich der milchweißen Linie folge</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Ao traçar a linha branco-leitosa</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Если пойти по молочно-белой линии</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Seguendo la linea color bianco latte</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Nyuuhaku no sen o tadottara</span></p>
      <p begin="01:15.730" end="01:20.650" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L13"><span begin="01:15.730" end="01:16.060">そう</span><span begin="01:16.160" end="01:16.800">か</span><span begin="01:16.900" end="01:17.120">こ</span><span begin="01:17.150" end="01:17.260">れ</span><span begin="01:17.320" end="01:17.990">が</span><span begin="01:18.090" end="01:18.680">私</span><span begin="01:18.780" end="01:19.090">の</span><span begin="01:19.570" end="01:19.780">欲</span><span begin="01:19.780" end="01:19.890">し</span><span begin="01:19.970" end="01:20.160">か</span><span begin="01:20.160" end="01:20.360">っ</span><span begin="01:20.360" end="01:20.650">た</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">这样啊 这才是我一直渴望的</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">這樣啊 這才是我一直渴望的</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">I see this was what I wanted</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">그렇구나, 이것이 내가 원했던</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Je vois c'était donc ça que je désirais</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Ya veo esto era lo que yo quería</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Ah das war es also was ich wollte</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Entendo então era isso que eu queria</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Вот как значит это то чего я желала</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Ah capisco era questo ciò che volevo</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Souka kore ga watashi no hoshikatta</span></p>
      <p begin="01:21.090" end="01:24.600" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L14"><span begin="01:21.090" end="01:21.800">小</span><span begin="01:21.890" end="01:22.160">規</span><span begin="01:22.280" end="01:22.540">模</span><span begin="01:22.680" end="01:22.900">な</span><span begin="01:22.900" end="01:22.940">宇</span><span begin="01:23.050" end="01:23.420">宙</span><span begin="01:23.420" end="01:23.530">を</span><span begin="01:23.670" end="01:23.960">統</span><span begin="01:24.030" end="01:24.240">べ</span><span begin="01:24.270" end="01:24.600">る</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">统御这小小宇宙的</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">統御這小小宇宙的</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Governing a small-scale universe</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">소규모의 우주를 아우르는</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Régnant sur un univers à petite échelle</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Gobernando un universo a pequeña escala</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Das unschuldige Strahlen</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Governando um universo em pequena escala</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Правящее этой маленькой вселенной</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Che governa un piccolo universo</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Shoukibo na uchuu o suberu</span></p>
      <p begin="01:25.020" end="01:29.760" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L15"><span begin="01:25.020" end="01:25.280">無</span><span begin="01:25.380" end="01:25.580">垢</span><span begin="01:25.630" end="01:25.910">の</span><span begin="01:26.280" end="01:27.560">輝</span><span begin="01:27.700" end="01:29.760">き</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">无暇的光辉</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">無瑕的光輝</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Innocent radiance</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">무구한 빛</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Un éclat d'une pureté immaculée</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Un resplandor inmaculado</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Das ein kleines Universum beherrscht</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">O brilho da inocência</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Невинное сияние</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Uno splendore innocente</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Muku no kagayaki</span></p>
      <p begin="01:47.280" end="01:53.710" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L16"><span begin="01:47.280" end="01:48.450">ドー</span><span begin="01:48.450" end="01:48.830">ル</span><span begin="01:51.090" end="01:51.320">知</span><span begin="01:51.320" end="01:51.510">っ</span><span begin="01:51.510" end="01:51.920">て</span><span begin="01:51.920" end="01:52.120">い</span><span begin="01:52.290" end="01:52.690">た</span><span begin="01:52.880" end="01:53.020">の</span><span begin="01:53.150" end="01:53.550">か</span><span begin="01:53.550" end="01:53.680">い</span><span begin="01:53.680" end="01:53.710">？</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">玩偶啊 你是早就知晓的吗</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">玩偶啊 你是早就知曉的嗎</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Doll did you know?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">인형아, 너는 알고 있었니?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Poupée le savais-tu ?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">¿Muñeca tú lo sabías?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Puppe hast du es gewusst?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Boneca você sabia?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Кукла знала ли ты об этом</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Bambola tu lo sapevi</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Dooru shitte ita no kai?</span></p>
      <p begin="01:55.740" end="01:59.760" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L17"><span begin="01:55.740" end="01:56.770">宝</span><span begin="01:56.920" end="01:57.290">の</span><span begin="01:57.290" end="01:57.670">在</span><span begin="01:57.760" end="01:58.680">処</span><span begin="01:58.840" end="01:59.760">で</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">在宝藏的所在之处</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">在寶藏的所在之處</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">At the whereabouts of the treasure</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">보물이 있는 곳에서</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Là où se trouve le trésor</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">En el escondite del tesoro</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Am Fundort des Schatzes</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">No esconderijo do tesouro</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Там где спрятано сокровище</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Nel luogo in cui si trova il tesoro</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Takara no arika de</span></p>
      <p begin="02:00.340" end="02:04.360" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L18"><span begin="02:00.340" end="02:01.060">共</span><span begin="02:01.150" end="02:01.400">に</span><span begin="02:01.530" end="02:01.790">寝</span><span begin="02:01.870" end="02:02.150">そ</span><span begin="02:02.290" end="02:03.120">べ</span><span begin="02:03.120" end="02:03.420">っ</span><span begin="02:03.420" end="02:04.360">て</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">与你一同并肩躺下</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">與你一同並肩躺下</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Lying down together</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">함께 엎드려 누워서는</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Allongées ensemble</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Acostadas juntas</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Gemeinsam liegend</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Deitando-nos juntas</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Мы лежали вместе</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Sdraiandoci insieme</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Tomo ni nesobette</span></p>
      <p begin="02:05.510" end="02:12.270" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L19"><span begin="02:05.510" end="02:06.590">育</span><span begin="02:06.590" end="02:06.910">っ</span><span begin="02:06.910" end="02:07.620">て</span><span begin="02:09.600" end="02:10.360">年</span><span begin="02:10.360" end="02:10.580">行</span><span begin="02:10.770" end="02:11.200">く</span><span begin="02:11.400" end="02:11.620">ほ</span><span begin="02:11.820" end="02:12.270">ど</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">随着不断成长岁月流逝</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">隨著不斷成長歲月流逝</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">The more I grow and age</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">자라나 나이를 먹어갈수록</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Plus je grandis et prends de l'âge</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Cuanto más crezco y envejezco</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Je mehr man wächst und älter wird</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Quanto mais cresço e envelheço</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Чем больше расту и взрослею</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Più si cresce e passano gli anni</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Sodatte toshi yuku hodo</span></p>
      <p begin="02:14.230" end="02:18.390" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L20"><span begin="02:14.230" end="02:14.860">脆</span><span begin="02:14.980" end="02:15.280">く</span><span begin="02:15.380" end="02:15.770">な</span><span begin="02:15.770" end="02:16.040">る</span><span begin="02:16.200" end="02:17.110">の</span><span begin="02:17.300" end="02:18.390">さ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">反而变得愈发脆弱</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">反而變得愈發脆弱</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">The more fragile I become</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">여려지는 거야</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Plus je deviens fragile</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Más frágil me vuelvo</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Desto zerbrechlicher wird man</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Mais frágil eu fico</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Тем более хрупкой становлюсь</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Più si diventa fragili</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Moroku naru no sa</span></p>
      <p begin="02:18.820" end="02:23.590" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L21"><span begin="02:18.820" end="02:19.100">向</span><span begin="02:19.190" end="02:19.560">け</span><span begin="02:19.590" end="02:19.930">ら</span><span begin="02:19.990" end="02:20.290">れ</span><span begin="02:20.390" end="02:20.670">た</span><span begin="02:20.780" end="02:21.790">愛</span><span begin="02:21.930" end="02:22.880">情</span><span begin="02:23.110" end="02:23.590">に</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">面对那倾注而来的爱意</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">面對那傾注而來的愛意</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">To the affection directed at me</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">나를 향해 쏟아지는 애정에</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Face à cette affection qui m'est adressée</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Por el afecto dirigido hacia mí</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Gegenüber der entgegengebrachten Liebe</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Ao afeto direcionado a mim</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">К обращенной на меня любви</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Dall'affetto che mi viene rivolto</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Mukerareta aijou ni</span></p>
      <p begin="02:24.220" end="02:32.900" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L22"><span begin="02:24.220" end="02:24.550">撫</span><span begin="02:24.620" end="02:24.990">で</span><span begin="02:24.990" end="02:25.390">る</span><span begin="02:25.390" end="02:26.090">よ</span><span begin="02:26.090" end="02:26.190">う</span><span begin="02:26.190" end="02:26.380">に</span><span begin="02:26.380" end="02:27.260">柔</span><span begin="02:27.260" end="02:27.540">い</span><span begin="02:27.540" end="02:28.240">二</span><span begin="02:28.310" end="02:28.420">つ</span><span begin="02:28.490" end="02:28.840">の</span><span begin="02:28.840" end="02:29.450">声</span><span begin="02:29.450" end="02:29.730">音</span><span begin="02:29.730" end="02:30.090">に</span><span begin="02:30.090" end="02:30.510">揺</span><span begin="02:30.830" end="02:31.210">ら</span><span begin="02:31.280" end="02:31.810">れ</span><span begin="02:31.980" end="02:32.330">て</span><span begin="02:32.360" end="02:32.900">る</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">在那宛如轻抚般柔和的两道声音中摇曳</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">在那宛如輕撫般柔和的兩道聲音中搖曳</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Swayed by two soft voices like a caress</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">어루만지듯 부드러운 두 목소리에 흔들리고 있어</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Je suis bercée par deux voix douces comme une caresse</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Me dejo mecer por dos voces tan suaves como una caricia</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Gewiegt von zwei sanften Stimmen die mich wie eine Liebkosung streicheln</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Sendo embalada por duas vozes macias como um carinho</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Укачиваемая двумя голосами нежными словно поглаживание</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Vengo cullata da due voci morbide come una carezza</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Naderu you ni yawai futatsu no kowane ni yurareteru</span></p>
      <p begin="02:33.790" end="02:43.910" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L23"><span begin="02:33.790" end="02:34.010">一</span><span begin="02:34.140" end="02:34.510">生</span><span begin="02:34.580" end="02:34.870">を</span><span begin="02:34.950" end="02:35.270">か</span><span begin="02:35.360" end="02:35.650">け</span><span begin="02:35.750" end="02:36.030">て</span><span begin="02:36.100" end="02:36.520">さ</span><span begin="02:36.520" end="02:36.660">え</span><span begin="02:36.750" end="02:36.920">見</span><span begin="02:36.920" end="02:37.110">当</span><span begin="02:37.270" end="02:37.640">た</span><span begin="02:37.660" end="02:37.900">ら</span><span begin="02:38.060" end="02:38.370">な</span><span begin="02:38.370" end="02:38.490">い</span><span begin="02:38.780" end="02:39.490">類</span><span begin="02:39.560" end="02:39.650">の</span><span begin="02:39.770" end="02:40.170">経</span><span begin="02:40.310" end="02:40.630">験</span><span begin="02:40.900" end="02:41.200">だ</span><span begin="02:41.200" end="02:41.490">っ</span><span begin="02:41.490" end="02:43.910">た</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">那是穷尽一生也难以寻觅的体验</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">那是窮盡一生也難以尋覓的體驗</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">It was the kind of experience you couldn't find even if you spent a lifetime</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">일생을 바친다 해도 찾아볼 수 없는 부류의 경험이었어</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">C'était le genre d'expérience introuvable même en y consacrant toute une vie</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Fue el tipo de experiencia que no encontraría ni dedicando toda mi vida</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Es war eine Art von Erfahrung die man selbst in einem ganzen Leben nicht findet</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Foi o tipo de experiência que não se encontra nem dedicando a vida inteira</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Это был опыт который не найти даже за целую жизнь</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">È stata un'esperienza tale che non si troverebbe nemmeno in una vita intera</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Isshou o kakete sae miataranai tagui no keiken datta</span></p>
      <p begin="02:46.140" end="02:50.260" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L24"><span begin="02:46.140" end="02:46.900">長</span><span begin="02:46.900" end="02:47.320">い</span><span begin="02:47.320" end="02:48.060">夢</span><span begin="02:48.100" end="02:48.380">の</span><span begin="02:48.520" end="02:49.550">中</span><span begin="02:49.630" end="02:50.260">で</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">在这漫长的梦境之中</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">在這漫長的夢境之中</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Inside a long dream</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">기나긴 꿈속에서 맞이한</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Dans un long rêve</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Dentro de un largo sueño</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">In einem langen Traum</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Dentro de um longo sonho</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">В долгом сне</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">In un lungo sogno</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Nagai yume no naka de</span></p>
      <p begin="02:50.570" end="02:54.680" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L25"><span begin="02:50.570" end="02:50.690">二</span><span begin="02:50.760" end="02:51.040">度</span><span begin="02:51.140" end="02:51.500">目</span><span begin="02:51.530" end="02:51.750">の</span><span begin="02:51.920" end="02:52.220">モ</span><span begin="02:52.290" end="02:52.810">ラ</span><span begin="02:52.890" end="02:53.100">ト</span><span begin="02:53.140" end="02:53.870">リ</span><span begin="02:53.870" end="02:54.140">ア</span><span begin="02:54.260" end="02:54.680">ム</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">迎来第二次的休憩期</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">迎來第二次的休憩期</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">A second moratorium</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">두 번째 유예의 시간</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Mon deuxième moratoire</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Una segunda moratoria</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Das zweite Moratorium</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">A segunda moratória</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Мой второй мораторий</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Una seconda moratoria</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Nidome no moratoriamu</span></p>
      <p begin="02:54.990" end="03:00.930" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L26"><span begin="02:54.990" end="02:55.290">どう</span><span begin="02:55.400" end="02:56.050">か</span><span begin="02:56.160" end="02:56.370">こ</span><span begin="02:56.400" end="02:56.510">れ</span><span begin="02:56.580" end="02:57.180">が</span><span begin="02:57.280" end="02:57.480">覚</span><span begin="02:57.550" end="02:57.630">め</span><span begin="02:57.730" end="02:57.910">て</span><span begin="02:58.050" end="02:58.330">も</span><span begin="02:58.790" end="02:59.050">消</span><span begin="02:59.200" end="02:59.480">さ</span><span begin="02:59.610" end="02:59.960">な</span><span begin="02:59.960" end="03:00.190">い</span><span begin="03:00.270" end="03:00.930">で</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">祈求你哪怕大梦初醒 也不要将其抹除</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">祈求你哪怕大夢初醒 也不要將其抹除</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Please don't erase this even when I wake up</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">부디 꿈에서 깨더라도 이것을 지우지 말아 줘</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Je t'en prie ne l'efface pas même si je m'éveille</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Por favor no borres esto aunque despierte</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Bitte lösche dies nicht aus selbst wenn ich erwache</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Por favor mesmo que eu acorde não apague isso</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Прошу не стирай это даже когда я проснусь</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Ti prego non cancellarlo anche quando mi sveglierò</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Douka kore ga samete mo kesanaide</span></p>
      <p begin="03:01.480" end="03:08.730" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L27"><span begin="03:01.480" end="03:02.040">人</span><span begin="03:02.620" end="03:03.340">生</span><span begin="03:03.790" end="03:04.100">を</span><span begin="03:04.410" end="03:04.890">歩</span><span begin="03:04.990" end="03:05.280">き</span><span begin="03:05.380" end="03:06.160">疲</span><span begin="03:06.190" end="03:06.460">れ</span><span begin="03:06.540" end="03:06.810">た</span><span begin="03:06.930" end="03:07.940">頃</span><span begin="03:08.100" end="03:08.730">に</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">当在这段人生旅途中走得疲惫不堪时</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">當在這段人生旅途中走得疲憊不堪時</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">When I get tired of walking through life</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">인생을 걸어가다 지칠 즈음에</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Quand je serai fatiguée de marcher à travers la vie</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Cuando esté cansada de caminar por la vida</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Wenn ich müde bin vom Gehen durchs Leben</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Quando eu estiver cansada de caminhar pela vida</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Когда я устану идти по жизни</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Quando sarò stanca di camminare nella vita</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Jinsei o arukitsukareta koro ni</span></p>
      <p begin="03:09.030" end="03:13.180" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L28"><span begin="03:09.030" end="03:09.960">再</span><span begin="03:09.990" end="03:10.300">び</span><span begin="03:10.360" end="03:10.520">こ</span><span begin="03:10.590" end="03:10.750">こ</span><span begin="03:10.800" end="03:11.300">で</span><span begin="03:11.350" end="03:11.620">出</span><span begin="03:11.620" end="03:12.320">逢</span><span begin="03:12.320" end="03:12.570">い</span><span begin="03:12.700" end="03:13.090">た</span><span begin="03:13.090" end="03:13.180">い</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">想要再次在这里与你相逢</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">想要再次在這裡與你相逢</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">I want to meet here again</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">다시 한번 이곳에서 만나고 싶어</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Je voudrais te rencontrer ici à nouveau</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Quiero que nos volvamos a encontrar aquí de nuevo</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Möchte ich dem hier wieder begegnen</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Quero me encontrar aqui novamente</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Я хочу встретиться здесь снова</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Voglio poterti incontrare di nuovo qui</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Futatabi koko de deaitai</span></p>
      <p begin="03:13.450" end="03:18.330" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L29"><span begin="03:13.450" end="03:13.790">遠</span><span begin="03:13.870" end="03:14.480">く</span><span begin="03:14.600" end="03:14.900">遠</span><span begin="03:15.000" end="03:15.720">く</span><span begin="03:15.720" end="03:16.150">忘</span><span begin="03:16.150" end="03:16.270">れ</span><span begin="03:16.410" end="03:16.740">て</span><span begin="03:17.070" end="03:17.170">し</span><span begin="03:17.290" end="03:17.470">ま</span><span begin="03:17.470" end="03:17.560">い</span><span begin="03:17.640" end="03:17.890">そ</span><span begin="03:17.890" end="03:18.080">う</span><span begin="03:18.080" end="03:18.330">な</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">那几乎要被远远遗忘的</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">那幾乎要被遠遠遺忘的</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Seemingly forgetting it far far away</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">아득히 머나먼 곳에 잊어버릴 것만 같은</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Si lointain si lointain que je pourrais presque l'oublier</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">A lo lejos muy a lo lejos como si fuera a olvidarlo</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Welches ich weit weit weg fast zu vergessen scheine</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">O qual parece que vou esquecer num lugar muito muito distante</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Такое далёкое далёкое что кажется вот-вот забудется</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Lontano lontano come se stessi per dimenticarlo</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Tooku tooku wasurete shimaisou na</span></p>
      <p begin="03:18.790" end="03:22.300" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L30"><span begin="03:18.790" end="03:19.510">小</span><span begin="03:19.600" end="03:19.870">規</span><span begin="03:19.990" end="03:20.280">模</span><span begin="03:20.370" end="03:20.600">な</span><span begin="03:20.600" end="03:20.660">宇</span><span begin="03:20.760" end="03:21.070">宙</span><span begin="03:21.070" end="03:21.230">を</span><span begin="03:21.350" end="03:21.640">占</span><span begin="03:21.730" end="03:21.940">め</span><span begin="03:21.970" end="03:22.300">る</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">占据这小小宇宙的</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">佔據這小小宇宙的</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Occupying a small-scale universe</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">소규모의 우주를 채우는</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Occupant un univers à petite échelle</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Ocupando un universo a pequeña escala</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Ein kleines Universum erfüllend</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Ocupando um universo em pequena escala</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Заполняющее эту маленькую вселенную</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Che occupa un piccolo universo</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Shoukibo na uchuu o shimeru</span></p>
      <p begin="03:22.700" end="03:27.500" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L31"><span begin="03:22.700" end="03:22.990">無</span><span begin="03:23.070" end="03:23.280">垢</span><span begin="03:23.350" end="03:23.620">の</span><span begin="03:24.010" end="03:25.370">輝</span><span begin="03:25.570" end="03:27.500">き</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">无暇的光辉</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">無瑕的光輝</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Innocent radiance</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">무구한 빛</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Un éclat d'une pureté immaculée</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Un resplandor inmaculado</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Das unschuldige Strahlen</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">O brilho da inocência</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Невинное сияние</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Uno splendore innocente</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Muku no kagayaki</span></p>
